---
import PublicLayout from '@layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about the history, formation and growth of St. Teresa of Kolkata Church, Paldane Parish."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section
    class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-28"
  >
    <!-- Gradient Background -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal-950 via-charcoal-900 to-primary-900"
    ></div>

    <!-- Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/35"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        About Our Parish
      </h1>

      <div class="w-24 h-[2px] bg-white mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full"></div>

      <p
        class="text-white/85 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto"
      >
        St. Teresa of Kolkata Church, Paldane is a vibrant Catholic parish built on faith, unity, and devotion to Christ.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">

      <!-- INTRO -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-4">
          Formation of Paldane Parish
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The parish was established to provide spiritual care and pastoral support to Catholic families in and around Paldane, fostering a strong and united faith community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- HISTORY CARDS -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-10 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-4">
            Foundation & Land Purchase (2004)
          </h3>

          <p class="text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            After consultations with parish leaders and representatives, the proposal to establish a new church at Paldane was approved to serve Catholic families in the region.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-5">
            Around one and a half acres of land was purchased and registered on <strong>19th March 2004</strong>. On the same day, the foundation stone was laid by <strong>Bishop Aloysius Paul D'Souza</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-10 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-4">
            Dedication to Blessed Teresa of Kolkata
          </h3>

          <p class="text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            The church was dedicated to <strong>Blessed Teresa of Kolkata</strong>, reflecting the devotion and wishes of the faithful.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal-700 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-5">
            Construction was completed through the dedicated efforts of parishioners, donors, and benefactors, marking a significant milestone in the parish’s history.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- TIMELINE -->
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-20">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 text-center mb-12">
          Parish Timeline
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-10">

          <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-[2px] bg-gray-300 flex-1 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm w-full">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
                April 2006 – Grand Preparations
              </h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                Extensive preparations were made for the inauguration, with committees formed and parishioners working together to ensure a meaningful celebration.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-[2px] bg-gray-300 flex-1 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm w-full">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
                24th April 2006 – Inauguration
              </h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                The church was blessed and inaugurated by <strong>Bishop Aloysius Paul D'Souza</strong>, followed by a thanksgiving Mass attended by clergy and faithful.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <div class="w-[2px] bg-gray-300 flex-1 mt-2"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm w-full">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
                13th August 2006 – Parish Declared Independent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                A decree formally declared Paldane Church an independent parish, serving approximately 250 Catholic families at the time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm w-full">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-2">
                Today – A Growing Faith Community
              </h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                The parish continues to grow in faith and unity, serving the spiritual needs of the faithful in Paldane and surrounding areas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PARISH HIGHLIGHTS -->
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-24">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-10 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal-900 mb-6">
            Parish Highlights
          </h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">
                Parish Established
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900">
                13th August 2006
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">
                Dedication
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900">
                St. Teresa of Kolkata
              </p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">
                Diocese
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-charcoal-900">
                Diocese of Mangalore
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
